metadata.name: Beave Jobs
metadata.description:
Each carefully crafted and detail-oriented piece of collectable 1/1 graphic art in THE ECCENTRIC BILLIONAIRES COLLECTION derives it's inspiration from the captivating and over-indulgent life of some of the world's richest individuals. 
-------
EACH piece has a number of easter eggs hidden throughout!
-------
This is an ongoing collection of ONLY 1/1.
-------

BEAVE JOBS depicts the eccentricities and style of the late, great Steve Jobs.  
-------
Created by: Ally Anderson (teh4lly4nderson)
